{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 License Criteria\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The first two contributors must agree on any criteria for terms on which the project can be relicensed. They must publish a dated statement of those criteria, or a dated statement that there are no criteria, together with the terms of this agreement, where potential contributors can find and read them. No contributor can relicense the project onto new terms that fail to meet the license criteria. Any contributor may change the license criteria by securing {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#supermajority"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
