{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Communications\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Equal Information\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Each contributor is entitled to receive each message sent to any other contributor under these terms.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Circulating Messages\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 To circulate a message under these terms, a contributor must send the message in the English language to each other contributor, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#retry"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
