{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Circulating Notices\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Any contributor who receives a notice under the terms of a relicensing must {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#circulating-messages"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
circulate
