{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Addresses\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The first two contributors must agree on a global, free or low-cost, high-speed, electronic communication system, such as e-mail, and provide addresses for that system. They must publish dated statement of that choice, together with the terms of this agreement, where potential contributors can find and read them. Later contributors must provide addresses for the same system.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Change of Address\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Any contributor may change their address by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#circulating-messages"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
circulating
}}}
 their new address from their current address. Alternatively, any contributor may change their address by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#circulating-messages"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
circulating
}}}
 their new address from a different address and securing {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#supermajority"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
supermajority approval
