{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Voting\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Equal Vote\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Each contributor is entitled to cast a single, equal vote on each proposal under these terms.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Majority\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 For majority approval, a majority of responding contributors must vote in favor.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Supermajority\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 For supermajority approval, two thirds of responding contributors must vote in favor.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Counting\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The contributor soliciting approval counts as a contributor voting in favor.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Deadline\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The deadline for approval of any proposal is thirty calendar days from when {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#soliciting-votes"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
votes were first solicited
}}}
.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Securing Approval\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 To secure an approval, a contributor must {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#soliciting-votes"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
solicit votes
}}}
, then {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#tallying-votes"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
tally votes
}}}
, and finally {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#reporting-results"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
report the result
}}}
.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Soliciting Votes\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 To solicit votes, a contributor must {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#circulating-messages"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
circulate
}}}
 a single message with all of these details:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab the identity of the project\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab the complete text of the proposal\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab the voting standard required\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab the date of the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#deadline"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
deadline
}}}
\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Casting Votes\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Contributors may vote by replying to a message soliciting votes using the same communication system. Messages like \u8220"I approve.\u8221", \u8220"I vote in favor.\u8221", and \u8220"Aye\u8221" count as votes in favor. Messages like \u8220"I oppose.\u8221", \u8220"I vote against.\u8221", and \u8220"Nay\u8221" count as votes against.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Tallying Votes\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 To tally votes, the contributor who solicited votes must ensure that each vote message is {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#circulating-messages"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
circulated
}}}
. If the communication system enables forwarding messages verbatim, such as by forwarding e-mail, the contributor must forward vote messages verbatim. If a voting contributor {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#circulating-messages"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
circulates
}}}
 their vote themself, the contributor soliciting votes need not {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#circulating-messages"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
circulate
}}}
 it again.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Reporting Results\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 To report a result, the contributor who solicited votes must {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#circulating-messages"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
circulate
}}}
 a single message with all of these details within seven calendar days after the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#deadline"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
deadline
}}}
:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab all the information required to {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#soliciting-votes"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
solicit votes
}}}
\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab copies of all {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#voting"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
vote messages
}}}
\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab counts of votes in favor, votes against, and contributors not responding by the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#deadline"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
deadline
}}}
\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab whether contributors approved the proposal or not\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Retry\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 When a {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#communications"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
