{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab The sending contributor must wait forty-eight hours, then try again. If the receiving contributor {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#change-of-address"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
